node.text: Karaoke tonight with friends. 🥰 We didn’t sing (I usually do), but it was so fun to sit in our little corner & hear people belt. Scott & I have been friends for nearly 20 years. I used to deliver his mail as an intern on The Tonight Show. Then, when I was happily thrust onto TV, he was there, guiding me every step of the way. We’ve been lifelong friends ever since. We should all be so lucky! ❤️
